  "description": "In Berlin, you could buy a döner on every corner. Unfortunately, there are just a few places that sell edible ones, and even there the quality is inconsistent. This is our homemade take on a slightly Mexicanized döner — *dönerrito*, a mix of a döner and a burrito.",
